            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iunoni <lb n="2"/>Nemesi <lb n="3"/>Eppius Martinus <lb n="4"/>et <expan><abbr>Mem</abbr><ex>mius</ex></expan> Esper <expan><abbr>tub</abbr><ex>icen</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Rodo et
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift ist unvollendet geblieben. In Zeile 4 tub(icen) oder tub(icines). (B): Z. 4. Weber-Hiden: vet(erani).</p>
